WARDEN CLANS

Long ago the clans were entrusted with defending the Inner Sphere by the Great Kerenksies. While our wayward brothers the Crusaders have forgotten this, we remember. Now as the Inner Sphere burns it is time for the Wardens to step in and save the Inner Sphere from itself. The genocidal Word of Blake and petty squabbling sucessor states are about to learn some fundemental truths, Don't poke the Bear and stay out of the water while the Diamond Shark is on the prowl...

Playable Subfactions:
<br>Clan Ghost Bear  (CGB)
<br>Clan Diamond Shark (CDS)
